Paciano: Jose, the tension here is growing. The friars are angered by your book.
Rizal: If my presence puts our family in danger, then I must leave again.
Paciano: When will you return?
Rizal: When the time is right.
"Marcelo H del Pilar": Rizal, your writings have inspired many Filipinos in Spain.
Rizal: We must continue pushing for reform through knowledge and reason.
"Graciano López Jaena": The Propaganda Movement needs strong voices.
Rizal: Then we will use our pens as our weapons.
"Marcelo H del Pilar": Spain must hear the truth about its colony.
Rizal: And one day, Filipinos will stand equal before the law.